{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents15OUDSAlertStatusO","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"enum","title":"OUDSAlertStatus","roleHeading":"Enumeration","modules":[{"name":"Components"}]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus"},"abstract":[{"text":"The status of the alerts.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertMessage"},{"type":"text","text":" background color and its icon color are based on this status."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInlineAlert"},{"type":"text","text":" icon and text color are based on this status."}],"topicSections":[{"title":"Enumeration Cases","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/accent(icon:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/info","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/negative","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/neutral(icon:)","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/positive","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/warning"],"anchor":"Enumeration-Cases","generated":true}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@frozen","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"There are two types of statuses:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Non-functional statuses used for informational or decorative alert messages.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"They provide context or highlight content without implying a specific state, system event, or user action.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"These alerts are not tied to UX patterns such as success, error, or warning, and may use contextual or brand-related icons to enhance recognition or storytelling.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Functional statuses communicate specific system statuses, results, or user feedback:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each variant conveys a clear semantic meaning and must always be paired with its dedicated functional icon to ensure clarity and accessibility.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Use functional alerts to inform user about state changes, confirmations, or issues that are directly connected to system logic or user actions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"These messages carry functional meaning and help guide user response or acknowledgment.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/neutral(icon:)":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Neutral status can be used as a generic informative alert without semantic meaning or colour association."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Suitable for a wide range of contexts — such as tips, general information, or descriptive labels — where"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"no specific feedback or urgency is required. Appropriate for help sections, dashboards, or onboarding flows."}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.neutral(icon:)","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/neutral(icon:)","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/neutral(icon:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"neutral"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"icon"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14OUDSComponents8OUDSIconV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"OUDSIcon"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/positive":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Positive status indicates that a task or process has been completed successfully. These alerts reassure users and confirm that no further action is needed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon."}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.positive","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/positive","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/positive","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"positive"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertMessage":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertMessage","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertmessage","title":"OUDSAlertMessage","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Alert message is a UI element that displays system feedback, status changes or required action; throughout detailed, prominent, persistent and actionable"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"communication. Alert message includes functional icon and semantic colour, and may include as well a close button and\/or action link."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Alert Message does not disappear automatically and remains visible until dismissed or resolved by the user."}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSAlertMessage","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSAlertMessage","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","title":"Components","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.SendableMetatype","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"OUDSAlertStatus","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSAlertStatus"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The status of the alerts."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertMessage"},{"type":"text","text":" background color and its icon color are based on this status."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInlineAlert","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" icon and text color are based on this status.","type":"text"}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSInlineAlert":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSInlineAlert"}],"title":"OUDSInlineAlert","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Inline alert is a lightweight UI element, placed in the content flow, that displays information, system feedback,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"status changes throughout short, prominent, persistent and non actionable communication. Inline alert includes functional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"icon and semantic colour, and does not include a close button and\/or action link. Inline alert does not disappear and remains visible."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSInlineAlert","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSInlineAlert"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsinlinealert","role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"Swift.Sendable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/accent(icon:)":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"accent"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"icon"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14OUDSComponents8OUDSIconV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"OUDSIcon"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Accent status uses brand colours to draw attention to promotional or highlighted information while remaining non-critical. Ideal for marketing content,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"announcements, or feature highlights, where you want to subtly engage users without introducing functional semantics. Ideal for promotional banners,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"product updates, or customer engagement moments.","type":"text"}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.accent(icon:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/accent(icon:)","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/accent(icon:)"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/negative":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Negative status communicates a critical issue or error that prevents the user from proceeding until it is resolved. These alerts remain visible until"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the problem is fixed or dismissed by the user."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon."}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.negative","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/negative","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/negative","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"negative"}]},"ic_folder_categories.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/ic_folder_categories.png"}],"identifier":"ic_folder_categories.png"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/info":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Info status is used to share neutral system information or service updates that do not require immediate action. Ideal for background processes or status"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"messages where users simply need to stay informed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon."}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.info","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/info","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/info","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"info"}]},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSAlertStatus/warning":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Used to draw attention to potential issues or upcoming changes that might affect the user’s service or experience. Warnings encourage awareness but"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"typically do not block actions."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This status displays a dedicated default icon."}],"title":"OUDSAlertStatus.warning","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsalertstatus\/warning","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSAlertStatus\/warning","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"warning"}]}}}